CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "The Gang's All Here! - Several died-in-the-wool picnickers can be identified in this shot at the Alpha Phi Alpha picnic at North Park last Friday..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three women, including two wearing striped dresses on left, and a man wearing ribbon inscribed "Guest...Picnic...North Park..." gathered at picnic table in North Park for Alpha Phi Alpha picnic
